originalText.text: If I can give a zero star I will.   First thing is that : Not clear about the price.  It’s kinda sneaky they only post 1/2 hr.   1 hr 2 hrs and jump to a 12 hrs option listed.  For a 2 hrs 11 mins parking I got charged for 12 hrs!!! I asked the man working at front to explain me the price again.  He is unbelievably rude and disrespectful. I would not recommend anyone to go here. Skip this awful place! STAY AWAY

Horrible experience parking at the garage. The keep the windows of all cars down and there ceiling is dripping all over the place. The brought out my car with stains all over the door and seat. I was told that I can submit a claim and talk to the manager the next morning. When called in the morning I was basically told to “bug off” and given a random number to call that never answers.

The parking attendants George and Cesar are the most rude and useless people. DO NOT PARK HERE!
